@model Vtb24.Arms.Security.Models.CustomFields.AppendCustomFieldModel
@using (Html.BeginForm("Append", "CustomFields", FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "modal hide", data_x = "security/customfields/append_modal" }))
{
    @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
    <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
        <h3>Создание дополнительного поля</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="span2 text-right"><span class="line-height-30">Наименование:</span></div>
            <div class="span5">
                @Html.TextBoxFor(m=>m.Name, new { @class="input-block-level", maxlength = 128 })
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(m=>m.Name)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Создать</button>
        <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Отменить</button>
    </div>
}
